"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus said that fighting in DR Congo is making it hard to stop the spread of diseases.\",            \"english_title\": \"Fighting in DR Congo\",            \"translated_version\": \"Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus dijo que las peleas en el Congo hacen dif\u00edcil parar las enfermedades.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Peleas en el Congo\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"At least three people died in an attack, even though there was supposed to be a ceasefire with Hamas.\",            \"english_title\": \"Attack Despite Ceasefire\",            \"translated_version\": \"Al menos tres personas murieron en un ataque, aunque deb\u00eda haber un alto el fuego con Hamas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataque a pesar de alto el fuego\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Nine people were hurt and nine more are missing after a tank broke at a paper mill in Longview, Washington.\",            \"english_title\": \"Accident at Paper Mill\",            \"translated_version\": \"Nueve personas resultaron heridas y nueve m\u00e1s est\u00e1n desaparecidas despu\u00e9s de que un tanque se rompi\u00f3 en una f\u00e1brica de papel en Longview, Washington.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Accidente en f\u00e1brica de papel\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Israel said it hit 100 Hezbollah sites and fighters in Lebanon after Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu promised to defeat the Iran-backed group.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israel Strikes Hezbollah\",            \"translated_version\": \"Israel dijo que atac\u00f3 100 sitios y luchadores de Hezbollah en L\u00edbano despu\u00e9s de que el Primer Ministro Benjamin Netanyahu prometi\u00f3 derrotar al grupo apoyado por Ir\u00e1n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Israel ataca a Hezbollah\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Italian Supreme Court said a tourist's consumer rights were not violated when she was only offered expensive bottled water.\",            \"english_title\": \"Tourist's Rights in Italy\",            \"translated_version\": \"La Corte Suprema de Italia dijo que los derechos del consumidor de una turista no fueron violados cuando solo le ofrecieron agua embotellada cara.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Derechos de turista en Italia\"        }    ]}"